725787f-b.title: Queens: 109th Road - 194th Street
725787f-b.text:
109th Road, south side, between 194th and 195th Streets, showing
in a set of two views the Odd Fellows Home. Owners of this property
were C. A. Colquit, 1860: A.J. Kerwin, 1873: and M. Fowmiger. The
gate posts bear the dates 1891 to 1913. Tenants and not owners were
the occupants of this place for yeame,
1923.
View 2: May 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
.E
w2
